Sentencas: Perovskite cathode material, (Ba0.5Sr0.5)(0.9)Bi0.1Co0.8Fe0.2O3-delta (BSBCF-0.1), was synthesized by a combined citrate-EDTA complexing method for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Synthesis and thermal expansion property of (Ba0.5Sr0.5)0.9Bi0.1Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ cathode materials for IT-SOFCs

Sentencas: Bi was successfully added to the perovskite structure.
Titulo: Synthesis and thermal expansion property of (Ba0.5Sr0.5)0.9Bi0.1Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ cathode materials for IT-SOFCs

Sentencas: A small amount of Bi could enter into the A-site of the perovskite structure, and ionic Bi would enter the B-site of the BSCF structure when the concentration was larger than 0.1.
Titulo: Synthesis and thermal expansion property of (Ba0.5Sr0.5)0.9Bi0.1Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ cathode materials for IT-SOFCs

Sentencas: Thermal expansion coefficient (TEC) of BSBCF-0.1 is lower than that of undoped BSCF in the working temperature range.
Titulo: Synthesis and thermal expansion property of (Ba0.5Sr0.5)0.9Bi0.1Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ cathode materials for IT-SOFCs

Sentencas: The decreased TEC of BSBCF may be more suitable for the thermal compatibility of cell components.
Titulo: Synthesis and thermal expansion property of (Ba0.5Sr0.5)0.9Bi0.1Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ cathode materials for IT-SOFCs

Sentencas: The maximum power density is 220 and 270 mW cm(-2) at 600 and 650 degrees C, respectively.
Titulo: Synthesis and thermal expansion property of (Ba0.5Sr0.5)0.9Bi0.1Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ cathode materials for IT-SOFCs

Sentencas: The result suggested that the perovskite BSBCF material could be considered as the cathode for IT-SOFCs.
Titulo: Synthesis and thermal expansion property of (Ba0.5Sr0.5)0.9Bi0.1Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ cathode materials for IT-SOFCs
